   World Markets:
   London Stocks Gain on Speculation of Early Entry
   Of Pound Into EMS Exchange-Rate Mechanism
   ----
   By Richard E. Rustin
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
06/13/90
</DATE>
